@node "Intro" "Description"
WarpDTPrefs is a preferences program which allows you to easily change and
manage the settings of the WarpJPEG, WarpPNG, WarpTIFF, WarpBMP, WarpPCX
and WarpPSD picture datatypes.

For information on the options present in the GUI, please read the relevant
sections in the documentation supplied with each datatype.
@endnode

@node "Requirements" "System Requirements"
WarpDTPrefs requires the following in order to work:

 - AmigaOS 3.5 or higher including resource.library
 - 68020 processor or higher, or suitable emulation
@endnode

